snippet.title: The Black Widow - Trailer / Indie Game 2019
snippet.description: Communicate with the dead using a spirit board to solve an actual murder case in this interactive mystery. Ask your own questions to determine whether “the Black Widow” was truly guilty … or unjustly executed.
